{"tid":1587202,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"不滿中国日益擴張  哈薩克爆反中示威","createTime":"2019-09-22T10:03:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T03:18:38.000Z","uid":184679,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fe28aa2724c8d8f9de3b3c97c0191afa22f944b7","tid":1587202,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T10:03:42.000Z","msg":"中國西北方的鄰國哈薩克，21日爆發街頭示威活動，訴求為反對中國對哈薩克影響力日增，以及表達對前總統宣布辭職後，卻仍大權在握的不滿。<br />\n<br />\n路透社報導，爆發示威的城市分別是首都努爾蘇丹（Nur-Sultan）及哈國最大城阿拉木圖（Almaty），在阿拉木圖，傳出有示威者被警方強行拖上警車；當局稱已拘留57人，並可能起訴這些被捕示威者。<br />\n<br />\n據報導，部分抗議者手持「我們不要讓中國擴張」標語，高呼反中國擴張口號，不滿中國對哈薩克影響力與日俱增；哈薩克人民也對一些遷移至當地的中國工廠表示反對，批評中企跟一些西方公司一樣，聘用太少當地人，而且工資也比外來工人低。<br />\n<br />\n哈國近年來反中情緒逐漸高漲，除了上述反對原因之外，中國在新疆的「去極端化」行動也可能是原因之一，因為被中國關進所謂「再教育營」的少數民族裡，部分就包含哈薩克族人。<br />\n<br />\n這場示威除了抗議中國外，同時也表達對前總統納札爾巴耶夫（Nursultan Nazarbayev）退休後仍大權在握的不滿。<br />\n<br />\n納札爾巴耶夫退位後，仍留任哈薩克安全委員會主席，並保留哈薩克執政黨「祖國之光」的黨內職位。<br />\n<br />\n納札爾巴耶夫在哈薩克執政將近30年，哈薩克經濟因2014年油價重挫受創，至今尚未恢復，導致近年社會不滿情緒升高。<br />\n<br />\n今年3月，納札爾巴耶夫突然宣布辭職，隨後6月的總統大選，則由他指定的接班人、時任代理總統托卡葉夫（Kassym-Jomart Tokayev）贏得選舉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201909220145.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F201909220145.aspx&d=AaXh75k8ef15jyN5JBlvBgmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=0bf6de5a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201909220145.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"4ad0827148e0132fbf424b154a052db42ff7a276","tid":1587202,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T10:05:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fa21899c532cd477a6f03283220212eff418f6a0","tid":1587202,"uid":318264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T10:06:38.000Z","msg":"全球反共勢不可檔<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3033961981266a254042405e6d563b96a15d2476","tid":1587202,"uid":216127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T10:06:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"87a6f121e652dbd91b2498ef551de4d2375fcee5","tid":1587202,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T10:08:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span><br />\n【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRrFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRrFcS</a>"},{"pid":"23036d0434856948bc1a9a8153cc307e5ed906cb","tid":1587202,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T10:22:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/offtopic.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/offtopic.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/offtopic.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/offtopic.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/offtopic.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46f5079aab24253fb059d560f73d814ffdedb0b0","tid":1587202,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T00:57:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32a8811ba67aba8faf61791c92bf29ae5045602d","tid":1587202,"uid":320078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T03:18:38.000Z","msg":"終於覺醒啦"}]}